title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
OB: The getcolumnlabel before extraction returns null labels, while the getcolumnlabel after extraction returns recognizable strings.
EB: When calling getcolumnlabel before extraction, it should return the same user recognizable labels as getcolumnlabel after extraction. This is important because the labels need to be displayed to the end user before performing extraction.
